==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Un-Romanized
<hw>Un-Ro"man*ized</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Not
subjected to Roman arms or customs.</def> <rj><au>J.
Whitaker.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Eccl.)</fld> <def>Not subjected to the principles
or usages of the Roman Catholic Church.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unroof</ent>⟦br⟧
